00:49:36,564 --> 00:49:38,521
It was a real statement to say,

740
00:49:38,646 --> 00:49:41,207
''Yes, I am willing to march
against the war.''

741
00:49:41,328 --> 00:49:44,880
When thousands of people did that,
it broke that consensus.

742
00:49:45,012 --> 00:49:48,086
That's what the anti-Vietnam War
movement did.

743
00:49:48,216 --> 00:49:49,888
It broke that consensus.

